divs: sighting detailson the 3rd of november, i observed slow moving, flashing lights high in the sky. these are the similar crafts that are rectangular in shape with the bright, flashing lights colored red and white! these lights however are not the lights you see on high flying airliners; they are much brighter and i have reported them in the past. as i watched the lights moving it went behind the tall tree in my neighbors yard. the light went behind it at the tip of the tree but came out the other side near the bottom of the tree and was much closer to the ground at this point. i observed this craft moving northward towards the mountains and eventually into oregon if it were to stay on that path. just when the lights were far enough away that i could still see the flashing lights but they were dimming because of trees and distance, it flashed brightly to where i actually pulled back and gasped because it felt like someone shot a bright light beam at me. this beam of light was felt in my left eye and not in my right eye. i say this because my left eye felt like it had looked at a welding light so i could feel the burn so to speak and slight discomfort. the weirdest part of this is that i saw or perceived an image ... a three pronged image; top and bottom with solid black in between. i had never seen this image that i can remember so i drew it so that i would not forget. some sort of ancient symbol of some sort is what i am getting out of this. . . and ancient alien symbol. i you go to http:\\ancientx.com\nm\anmviewer.asp?a=90 you'll see the three pronged symbol on the piece that was left behind as part of the debris from the roswell incident and crash. i was not aware of this until i searched for the symbol. i felt unusually tired the next two days and my eye felt some trauma but no burn of any kind was left and has since healed from the discomfort.
Summary: While observing slow moving lights to the north was zapped by beam with a symbol
